		"description": "<p>You magically create a minor electrical pulse that can either provide temporary power to a small contraption or numb a creature&rsquo;s hand.</p>\n<p>You reach out and touch a target creature, producing a small electrical charge that jolts into them. The target makes a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failure, they immediately drop their weapon or other item that they are carrying as their hand becomes numb. If the target is wielding a weapon in both hands (such as a spear or a great sword) they make their save at advantage.</p>\n<p>If the spell is used to power a small contraption, it provides enough electrical impulse to power said object for up to 1 minute.</p>",
